Show - Class in View
 
Show() - Constructor for class View.Show
 
show_card(Card) - Static method in class View.Show
Observer: Displays the given Card on to a JOptionPane Panel.
showDealCards(Card) - Static method in class View.Show
Observer: Displays the given Deal Card on to a JOptionPane Panel without a Choice.
showDialoge(String) - Static method in class View.Show
Observer: Displays the given message on to a JOptionPane Panel
postcondition: Displays the given message from a JOptionPane Panel.
showFootbalMatch() - Static method in class View.Show
Observer: Creates a JOptionPane Panel and returns the Players Choice.
showSellCard(Card) - Static method in class View.Show
Observer: Displays the given Deal Card on to a JOptionPane Panel with the choices sell and Next Card.
shuffle(Pack_of_cards) - Static method in class Controller.Controller
Observer: Shuffles and put all the Cards from the Pile to the Main stack (Mail or Deal).
Start() - Static method in class Controller.Controller
observer: Takes all the necessary information from the user , initializes all the necessary Components(Players, Cards, Positions), creates the main Frame and then Starts the game
post-conditions: Asks for the Months, then creates the Pack of Cards, Player 1, Player 2, Board and BoardGUI and then Rolls Dice for both Players anf gives the first turn to the Player with the highest Dice.
Sunday_Match(Player) - Static method in class Controller.Controller
observer: Asks the player if he wants to bet for a football match if he wins it he gains 500 euros else he loses 500 euros (this method is called only when in certain positions on the board)
post-conditions: Asks the Player P1 if he wants to bet, if he wins he 500 are added to his Money if he loses 500 are removed from his Money
Sweepstakes - Class in Model.Position
